import './Doctor.css'; export default function Doctor(props) { //https://ep-doctor-api.herokuapp.com/doctors const { name, last_name, photo, specialty_1, specialty_2, medical_school, years_in_practice, practice_name, drug_list, availability} = props.doctor; return (

Dr. {name} {last_name}, MD

Main Specialty: {specialty_1}
Secondary Specialty: {specialty_2 ? specialty_2 : "Not Available"}
Medical School: {medical_school}
Years In Practice: {years_in_practice}
Current Practice/Hospital: {practice_name}
Doctor is a high prescriber and can discuss:
{drug_list.join(", ")}

Doctor's Availability

Monday:
Tuesday:
Wednesday:
Thursday:
Friday:
) }
